===Noun===
'''Negro''' or '''negro'''

#(Often capitalized) A person of [[African]] descent, with [[negroid]] coloring and facial characteristics.  (Note that [[black]] appears to be the currently preferred term for Negros in the US.)

====Translation====
* German: [[Neger]] ''m'', [[Negerin]] ''f''
* Slovak: [[černoch]] ''m'', [[černoška]] ''f''
* Spanish: [[negro]] ''m'', [[negra]] ''f''

